        "timestamp": 1716322065
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>atkal savākušies daži<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/fxPzck2ICwlIun-aZpbQ6I9o/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/fxPzck2ICwlIun-aZpbQ6I9o/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/49624/fxPzck2ICwlIun-aZpbQ6I9o/image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>[out:xml][timeout:90];\n{{geocodeArea:Latvia}}-&gt;.searchArea;\n(\n  relation[type=multipolygon](if:count_members()==1)(area.searchArea);\n);\n(._;&gt;;);\nout meta;\n</code></pre></div>",
