    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Un barrier fence pa virsu 🤦🏻🤦🏻🤦🏻</p>",
        "id": 577710353,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1772792072
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>kur citur tos žogus likt?</p>",
        "id": 577710523,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792116
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Kāpēc vājag taisīt mēslu kur var rejuzot ways in relation?</p>",
        "id": 577710579,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1772792130
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Cilvēki nemāk izmanot relations/multipolygonus un taisa sūdus ar šādiem pluginiem/datiem 🤷🏻 imho</p>",
        "id": 577711004,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1772792241
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>man personīgi daudz vieglāk ir bez relācijām<br>\nkāpēc izmantot 3 way'us ja var ar 1 area<br>\nžogus pa virsu zīmēt piekrītu ka ir stulbi bet taisīt no daudziem maziem gabaliņiem relācijas ir murgs</p>",
        "id": 577711890,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792492
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/One_feature,_one_OSM_element\">https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/One_feature,_one_OSM_element</a></p>",
        "id": 577711991,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792527
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Man kā oo programmētāju mācīja atkārtoti izmantot objektus, nevis taisīt katru atsevišķi</p>",
        "id": 577712341,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1772792623
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"572039\">Colby</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/358602-general/topic/Multipoligoni/near/577711991\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/One_feature,_one_OSM_element\">https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/One_feature,_one_OSM_element</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>A feature that consists of several smaller features is usually best described using a relation</p>",
        "id": 577712686,
        "sender_full_name": "UrSuS",
        "timestamp": 1772792719
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>tam turpinājums:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>For example, <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Relation:route\">relation:route</a> for a hiking route</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>ok</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A closed way tagged with two feature tags, one of which is usually a linear feature such as <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Abarrier%3Dhedge\">barrier=hedge</a> and another which represents an area such as <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Aamenity%3Dschool\">amenity=school</a>. In this case it is ambiguous if the barrier is meant to represent an area or a line, and for all properties it is unclear to which feature they belong. In such a case you may consider making a separate relation relation for the <a href=\"https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Tag%3Aamenity%3Dschool%3A\">amenity=school:</a> make the closed way area an role outer member of the relation and transfer the educational tags from the way area to the relevant relation relation.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 577713080,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792823
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>ideālā pasaulē OSM datu formāts būtu tāds ka multipoligonus nevajadzētu vispār</p>",
        "id": 577713466,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792929
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>kā tas jau ir ar visādiem .shp un citem</p>",
        "id": 577713549,
        "sender_full_name": "Colby",
        "timestamp": 1772792944
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Izmantot tos pašus objektus ir labi, ja tie tiks tikai savstarpēji aiztikti (piemēram robežas). Bet kā jau daudzās citās tēmās minēts, praksē tas tā nestrādā ar mainīgām lietām. Tagad tikai pēc 10 gadiem jau cik no tiem senajiem multipoligoniem ir nepareizi. Ceļi tiek pārbūvēti, grāvji pārrakti, robežas nobīdītas, krasti izskaloti, meži izcirsti, kadastra vienības izmainītas, utt. Tad tur izrādās daļa sētas ir siena, daļa grāvja ir caurteka, daļa meža ir stiga, daļa zemes ir komerciāla un pēkšņi kaut kāds vienkāršs taisnstūris zāles pleķis sastāv no 20 ceļiem. Un, ja tur kaut kas izmainās, neviens to nekad vairs nelabos, noteikti ne jauni kartētāji.</p>",
        "id": 577722154,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1772795395
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Un žogam lielisks piemērs tajā pašā vietā ir <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1087348049\">https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1087348049</a> - nepareizi žogs kopā ar mājas sienu, jo parasti tādus vieglāk bija pielikt tegus pa virsu visam area/multipoligoniem nekā iezīmēt pareizi. Es daudz dzirdu, ka vajag tikai JOSM mācēt to izdarīt un viss būs forši. Bet es ļoti reti redzu, lai kāds to arī reāli darītu. It īpaši pēc tam, kad vajag izlabot.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1087348049\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/6216f4773cbede236f0589ddcc1cf59e83a3b7bb/68747470733a2f2f7777772e6f70656e7374726565746d61702e6f72672f6173736574732f6f736d5f6c6f676f5f3235362d656430323866393034363832323461323732393631633338306563656530636662373362383034386233346634623462323034623766306431303937383735642e706e67&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/1087348049\" title=\"Way: 1087348049\">Way: 1087348049</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">OpenStreetMap is a map of the world, created by people like you and free to use under an open license.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 577723542,
        "sender_full_name": "HellMap",
        "timestamp": 1772795791
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Bildīte arhīvam pirms izlabots <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/a21oxw3T17jUQBNjITKCjZwt/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/49624/a21oxw3T17jUQBNjITKCjZwt/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"632x594\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/49624/a21oxw3T17jUQBNjITKCjZwt/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
